Emily Lloyd https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Lloyd 0 Emily Lloyd-Pack (born 29 September 1970), known as Emily Lloyd, is an English actress, perhaps best known for her breakthrough performance at the age of sixteen in the 1987 David Leland film Wish You Were Here, for which she received critical acclaim.
